page.title: 16S.E.Grantham Domesday Help
page.content:
The following members of St Wulfram's Comprehensive School helped to collect information for the Domesday Project. Stephen Taylor Colin Pattison Elliott Clark Mark Hands Richard Broughton Andrew Rawlinson Peter Severn Sarah Dring Darren Hardingham David Hoyes Paul Woolerton Donna Corby Tracey Love Andrea Wilson Gary Campbell Tony Claasen Christopher Love Paul Squires Jason Watson Ruth Amis Lynne Berridge Lisa Mallinder Sarah Parkinson Richard Alderton Emma Longrigg Katie Thompson Paul Freestone Michael Honeybone
The work was carried out in November and December 1985.
